 hadronic medium, 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "R.-Rapp:2000uq,Cassing199965,Gale:2003qv,Alam2000159"

\end_inset

.
 These calculation based on hadronic many-body interactions predict a strong
 broadening of the 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

